"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/35/14905?source=see_link\">",
"      Cytogenetics and molecular genetics of myelodysplastic syndromes",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/40/17030?source=see_link\">",
